reviews.comment: I had the pleasure of working with Usman for this project. He is very polite and prompt. A great guy. The website delivered was as expected, nothing more nothing less. While I did receive a functional and decent website. I was kind of thrown off when I noticed it was basically just a filled in Wordpress template. But it worked out so I guess I’m okay with it. I wouldn’t pay $500 for this again though.

Overall the experience was average. Quite good creatively, but in terms of communication and ability to implement revisions changes, not good. Individually labelled revision points were ignored or disregarded (without any explanation) while others were competed. Was also charged more halfway through, even though I was very clear about scope and references at the beginning. Took much longer than anticipated also. Could not recommend.

I am blown away with my new website and can not wait to launch my new design company. This has been one of the easiest experiences I have ever had working with someone. Usman is super talented and was able to create something truly special for me.

Created a good up-to-date website for me. Took longer than expected because of either not understanding requests well or his lack of attention to detail (he estimated 1-2 weeks but it took 70 days). Still very happy with the website. Great guy, very polite, hard worker.

I always find building a website and starting a business very frustrating in the beginning as bringing a vision to life and trying to get that information across isn't easy. But the end result is something that I am so happy about and the website is absolutely fantastic, and exactly how I wanted it to be. I will definitely be using you again to further grow our business in the future. All the best, Jack - wereallfriends.com
I'm really Happy to work with wordpress_play, He described me all the things in proper way and provide me all things that I need. In future I will be Happy to work again with wordpress_play.
